data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION!  This ONE OWNER  ALL BRICK RANCH patio home in the popular community of The Enclave won't last long.  This is a great little neighborhood in the HEART of Fort Collins. It's rare to find a low maintenance home, backing to greenbelt, in a quiet cul-de-sac, yet also close to shopping, parks, bike paths, restaurants, and two golf courses (Colindale & Southridge).  Enjoy the primary suite, with a large walk-in closet and primary bath w/ a sizable walk-in shower.  The other room on the main floor can be an office or 2nd bedroom (w/wood floors). Main level laundry, or second set of laundry hook-ups in the basement.  The basement has an over-sized guest suite, w/ sitting area, large walk-in closet & full bath.  The remainder of the basement is an unfinished room for storage convenience or for customizing by the new owners!  There is a covered patio for enjoying the outside area which is maintained by the HOA. Enjoy the 2-car attached garage, the granite in the kitchen & main bath, expansive and open living room/dining room space, bright welcoming glass patio doors to the backyard, & much more! HOA includes snow removal (including driveway), landscaping, some exterior maintenance, & trash (details to be verified by buyer). Pets & backyard fence allowed (see HOA docs for details). Come take a look before it's gone!
